						               													<description>Publishers summary&amp;#10;&amp;#227;&amp;#131;&amp;#152;&amp;#227;&amp;#131;&amp;#171;&amp;#227;&amp;#131;&amp;#136;&amp;#227;&amp;#130;&amp;#166;&amp;#227;&amp;#130;&amp;#175;&amp;#227;&amp;#131;&amp;#179; (Herutoukun) HELLTOKEN: REMOTE CONTROL ROBOT is a Japanese game with two secret societies both operating the same giant robot by remote control. The giant robot has been built by Dr Mad, who sells it for 100m Bitcoin. The two buyers are evil organizations aiming for world conquest,&amp;#10;&amp;#233;&amp;#173;&amp;#148;&amp;#232;&amp;#161;&amp;#147;&amp;#231;&amp;#181;&amp;#144;&amp;#231;&amp;#164;&amp;#190;&amp;#227;&amp;#131;&amp;#161;&amp;#227;&amp;#131;&amp;#162;&amp;#227;&amp;#131;&amp;#172;&amp;#227;&amp;#131;&amp;#188;&amp;#227;&amp;#131;&amp;#168; (Magical Association Memorireo) and &amp;#227;&amp;#131;&amp;#158;&amp;#227;&amp;#130;&amp;#185;&amp;#227;&amp;#131;&amp;#137;&amp;#227;&amp;#131;&amp;#172;&amp;#227;&amp;#131;&amp;#128;&amp;#227;&amp;#131;&amp;#188;&amp;#231;&amp;#167;&amp;#145;&amp;#229;&amp;#173;&amp;#166;&amp;#232;&amp;#178;&amp;#161;&amp;#229;&amp;#155;&amp;#163; (Masudoreda Science Foundation). Since he only built one robot, Dr Mad lets the two groups fight for it, using the robot.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Helltoken, all players control the same robot. You either try to crush the opponent's base, or deduce where your own hidden base is.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is easily to play by all, even those who have a hard time deducing! And the art is done by Takashi Kurihara, of 'Katamari Damacy' fame!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
